text: Ladda Duanchai (born 3 October 1980) is a Thai volleyball player. She played for the Thai women's national volleyball team. She participated at the FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2001 Universiade, 2002 FIVB World Grand Prix. == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Thai sportspeople Category:Volleyball players
